snippet.title: The Sims 4: Get Famous Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Experience the celebrity lifestyle with your Sims! Build your stardom as you pursue an acting career, become an A-lister, and guide your Sims down the unpredictable path to fame. Reach for the stars and rise to celebrity status.

Available November 16, 2018 for PC and Mac.

Learn more about this Expansion Pack: http://x.ea.com/50852.

*REQUIRES THE SIMS 4 GAME (SOLD SEPARATELY) AND ALL GAME UPDATES TO PLAY. SEE www.thesims.com/system-requirements FOR MINIMUM SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS FOR THIS PACK.

#sims4 #getfamous
